{"tid":162952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無待堂：援助旺角事件被告的聯絡轉介服務","createTime":"2017-03-19T15:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T14:33:52.000Z","uid":34147,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9662a72a7e1aa999923aa76e7e0cbd7607be55b0","tid":162952,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳：援助旺角事件被告的聯絡轉介服務】<br />\n<br />\n接觸了一些協助第三被告薜達榮的義工，我得到其同意，向各位提供一些薜先生的情況。薜先生是家中經濟支柱，母親有糖尿病，入獄前每月支付家用八千元；他還有一個精神有問題的哥哥需要照顧。<br />\n<br />\n薜先生一家急須應急資金，申請綜援是有計劃的，到成功拿到錢，起碼需要幾個月，是否上訴應該還在研究。薜達榮表示如外界有緩助，他們會收取。<br />\n<br />\n除了我自己捐款，我不會沾手其他的事情，只是做一個聯絡人的角色，在這個Case上，如果大家希望實際上金援示威者一家，其中一個辦法是私信我的專頁或者個人帳戶，我會將閣下直接轉介給跟進事情的義工朋友，由你們直接洽談，盡量避免事情牽涉太多政治、傳媒或者純粹是我的個人影響，避免有任何行政費或者抽成。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何提問，可以私信查詢，我作為義務的聯絡人會盡快答覆。聯絡資訊絕對保密，感謝各位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1299827623436313&amp;id=204247792994307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1299827623436313%26id%3D204247792994307&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4f5e19f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1299827623436313&amp;id=204247792994307</a><br />\n<br />\nfyi：無待堂，即係堂主盧斯達，信唔信任堂主各位自己決定。"},{"pid":"81f019bd4bb19425ad2cb7c8314acadd787a0690","tid":162952,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"896dec8a8087ec457babfaa7223ca658252347bc","tid":162952,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801ab1da95d436e26eb8032c431dff73d032fabd","tid":162952,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4772f3b46b618fb904bd0672abbc20320c53b0b1","tid":162952,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8727512562a386ab257b01bddf5d6e7993dac2b0","tid":162952,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"更新（其實係19號嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nFacebook Kelvin Ko: <br />\n向暴動罪三位被告嘅相關人士了解過, 由於現階段需要等法援審批有關上訴訟費嘅申請, 過程需要半年到, 所以訟費唔係三位最迫切要解決嘅問題. 各位想捐錢嘅朋友可以儲住先.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154929214635336&amp;id=550120335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10154929214635336%26id%3D550120335&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f1128e63\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10154929214635336&amp;id=550120335</a>"},{"pid":"695052fb146593c3d14ad02d77c9c418e2b4d03a","tid":162952,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9582a7e31735b629e52aa6fb437d68d8f338b8cf","tid":162952,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6d060c728f8cf93173d3dba0b5b23ecd59289c","tid":162952,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"119d1c494f1a35a6362fd9bcd542d95f845ee584","tid":162952,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4fc1ec5fa117c27d6fe7dd69bd853bd9cb3d55","tid":162952,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"做乜碌撚話叫人有野搵佢就比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\